quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,222,"La k steqsayen $ef tarda. Ini: \"d aîan. Âazlet tilawin di tarda, ur pqeôôibet $uôsent alamma ûfant. Mi ûfant, qeôôbet $uôsent, akken i wen Iumeô Öebbi\". Ih, Öebbi Iêemmel wid iutuben, Iêemmel wid izzizdigen"
  2,223,"Tilawin nnwen d aêôiq n tyerza nnwen. Melmi teb$am, aset s aêôiq nnwen. Zzewret lxiô i yiman nnwen, êezzbet i Öebbi. Cfut ar kunwi a T temmagrem. Becceô lmumnin"
  2,224,"Ur ssekcamet Öebbi mara teggallem a ppizdigem, a pêezzbem, a ppessemûalêem medden. Öebbi Issel, d Amusnaw"
  2,225,"Ur kwen Ipqissi ara Öebbi $ef tgallit $ef awal. Maca, a kwen Iqiss $ef wayen kesben wulawen nnwen. Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Iêellem"
  2,226,"Wid iggullen ur pqeôôiben ar tlawin nnsen, ad gganin kué wagguren. Ma bedlen ôôay, ihi, Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  2,227,"Ma âazmen berru, ihi, Öebbi Issel, d Amusnaw"
  2,228,"Timnufaq ad aôount krav tardiwin. Ur asent iêell ara ad ffrent ayen Ixleq Öebbi, di tâabbav nnsent, ma umnent s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru. Ma b$an irgazen nnsent ad mûalaêen, izzewr iten lêal a tent id rren, di lmudda nni. Akken pwalasent ay ppalasent, s lqanun. I yirgazen, asurif $er loiha nnsent. Öebbi d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab"